@page "/"
@layout HomeLayout

<PageTitle>Ai-My - AI-Powered CV and Creative Tools</PageTitle>

<div class="home-container">
    <header class="welcome-section">
        <h1>Welcome to Ai-My</h1>
        <p class="lead">Choose a service below to get started with AI-powered assistance</p>
    </header>

    <section class="services-section">
        <details class="expandable-section job-applications-section" open aria-label="Job Applications accordion">
            <summary id="job-apps-summary" role="button" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="job-apps-content">
                <span class="section-title">Job Applications</span>
            </summary>
            <div id="job-apps-content" class="page-tiles" role="region" aria-labelledby="job-apps-summary">
                <a href="/ReviewCV" class="page-tile review-cv-tile" aria-describedby="review-cv-desc">
                    <div class="tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">📎</div>
                    <div class="tile-title">Review your CV</div>
                    <div class="tile-description" id="review-cv-desc">Get AI-powered feedback to improve your CV</div>
                </a>

                <a href="/CoverLetter" class="page-tile cover-letter-tile" aria-describedby="cover-letter-desc">
                    <div class="tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">✉️</div>
                    <div class="tile-title">Cover Letter</div>
                    <div class="tile-description" id="cover-letter-desc">Create customized cover letters for job applications</div>
                </a>

                <a href="/CustomiseCV" class="page-tile customise-cv-tile" aria-describedby="customise-cv-desc">
                    <div class="tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">📄</div>
                    <div class="tile-title">Customise CV</div>
                    <div class="tile-description" id="customise-cv-desc">Tailor your CV to specific job descriptions</div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </details>

        <details class="expandable-section arts-and-crafts-section" open aria-label="Arts and Crafts Applications accordion">
            <summary id="arts-crafts-summary" role="button" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="arts-crafts-content">
                <span class="section-title">Arts and Crafts Applications</span>
            </summary>
            <div id="arts-crafts-content" class="page-tiles" role="region" aria-labelledby="arts-crafts-summary">
                <a href="/ColouringPage" class="page-tile colouring-page-tile" aria-describedby="coloring-desc">
                    <div class="tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">🖼️</div>
                    <div class="tile-title">Colouring Page</div>
                    <div class="tile-description" id="coloring-desc">Transform photos into printable coloring pages</div>
                </a>

                <a href="/SewingPattern" class="page-tile sewing-page-tile" aria-describedby="sewing-desc">
                    <div class="tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">✂️</div>
                    <div class="tile-title">Sewing Pattern</div>
                    <div class="tile-description" id="sewing-desc">Create sewing patterns from clothing images</div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </details>
    </section>

    <section class="faqs-section" aria-label="Frequently Asked Questions">
        <details class="faq-accordion" aria-label="Tool FAQs">
            <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqs-content" id="faqs-summary">FAQs</summary>
            <div id="faqs-content" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqs-summary">
                <h3>Review CV</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>What file types are supported?</strong> PDF, DOCX, and TXT up to 10MB.</li>
                    <li><strong>Is my data stored?</strong> Files are processed to generate feedback; avoid sensitive data. See the Privacy page for details.</li>
                    <li><strong>How do I get best results?</strong> Use a clean, text-based CV and a clear target role or job description.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Cover Letter</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Do I need a job description?</strong> Yes, provide a JD or role summary to tailor the letter.</li>
                    <li><strong>Can I change tone or length?</strong> Yes, you can refine and regenerate with guidance.</li>
                    <li><strong>Which languages are supported?</strong> English is best; other languages may vary in quality.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Customise CV</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>What should I upload?</strong> Your current CV and the target job description.</li>
                    <li><strong>What output do I get?</strong> Actionable edits, suggested bullet points, and skill alignment tips.</li>
                    <li><strong>Can I export the result?</strong> Copy the suggestions and apply them to your CV editor of choice.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Colouring Page</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>What images work best?</strong> High-contrast photos with clear subjects produce cleaner lines.</li>
                    <li><strong>What is the size limit?</strong> Up to 10MB. Use JPG or PNG.</li>
                    <li><strong>What do I get back?</strong> A black-and-white image ready to print and color.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Sewing Pattern</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>How accurate are the patterns?</strong> Suitable for prototyping; always adjust with test fabric.</li>
                    <li><strong>What images should I use?</strong> Well-lit, front-facing photos with minimal background clutter.</li>
                    <li><strong>Do you include measurements?</strong> Provide a reference (e.g., known width) for better scale guidance.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </details>
    </section>
</div>